dcterms:creator: B. Ashuri
J. Lu
dcterms:description: The Construction Cost Index (CCI) is published once a month by Engineering Cost Record (ENR). For the purpose of forecasting time series, 295 CCI data values (CCI data sets from January 1990 to July 2014) were employed. In the experiment, CCI divided the time series into training data sets and forecasting data sets in an 8:2 ratio.
dcterms:title: Construction Cost Index (CCI)
